{{!
    @template mod_glaaster/return_framebreak

    Frame-break page shown when an embedded LTI tool completes.
    The AMD module return_framebreak.js handles the actual redirect.
    The noscript block provides a fallback link for no-JS environments.

    Classes required for JS:
    * none

    Data attributes required for JS:
    * none

    Context variables required for this template:
    * clickhere - localised "click here to continue" link HTML

    Example context (json):
    {
        "clickhere": "<a href=\"/course/view.php?id=1\">Return to course</a>"
    }
}}
<noscript>
    {{{clickhere}}}
</noscript>
